<p><strong>坠星者</strong></p>
<p><strong>发布时间：</strong>2018年9月27日</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609563146" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span>，进入<a href="/lyricslinn-s-personnel-file">人事档案</a>查看该名作者的更多作品</p>
<p><strong>翻译：</strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/falling-into-stars">点此查看主站发布版</a>，感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jochoi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4255421); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4255421&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609563146" alt="Jochoi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4255421)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jochoi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4255421); return false;">Jochoi</a></span>的翻译和<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-lancelot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3494246); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3494246&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609563146" alt="A Lancelot" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3494246)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-lancelot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3494246); return false;">A Lancelot</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/star-lyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5096130); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5096130&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609563146" alt="Star Lyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5096130)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/star-lyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5096130); return false;">Star Lyn</a></span>的协助！！！<span style="color: transparent">呜哇，好高兴qwq</span></p>
